Third-party content and licensing notes
========================================

This MIT license covers the original source code of the Bambu-Spoolman-Bridge
in this repository (app/, scripts/, web/). It does NOT relicense third-party
material that the tooling interacts with:

- Filament presets generated by scripts/build_catalog.py and app/preset_gen.py
  are derived at runtime from locally installed BambuStudio / OrcaSlicer
  profiles, which are licensed under AGPL-3.0. Such generated catalogs are
  produced on the user's machine and are NOT distributed as part of this
  repository. If you redistribute generated preset data, the AGPL-3.0 terms of
  the source profiles apply to that data.
- SpoolmanDB data (https://github.com/Donkie/SpoolmanDB) is MIT-licensed and is
  fetched at runtime, not vendored here.
- The Bambu Lab network plugin (libbambu_networking.*) is closed-source and is
  neither included nor redistributed; only observations of one's own account
  data are used.
